Program: Discovery
Title: Sir John Maddox
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwkk
Last Broadcast Date: 14 December 1995
Influence of Sir John Maddox, editor of the scientific journal Nature. Since 1966 until last month Sir John has been at the helm of science's most influential publication. He talks about the era in which he edited the magazine and the highlights of his career.